OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1782371886
OL,3,CTranscript reveals moment police
OL,4,Cdiscovered Henry Nowak had been stabbed
OL,6,FPolice officers who arrested Henry
OL,7,FNowak in his final moments took around
OL,8,Feight minutes to discover his stab
OL,9,Fwound, newly-released evidence shows.
OL,11,FVickrum Digwa, 23, was jailed for life
OL,12,Fwith a minimum term of 21 years on
OL,13,FJune 1 for the murder of the 18-year-
OL,14,Fold finance student, after falsely
OL,15,Fclaiming Mr Nowak had racially abused
OL,16,Fhim.
