CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1782371886
OL,3,CTranscript reveals moment police
OL,4,Cdiscovered Henry Nowak had been stabbed
OL,6,FAnger erupted after a three-minute
OL,7,Fpolice body-worn video was released
OL,8,Fshowing Mr Nowak, from Chafford
OL,9,FHundred, Essex, being placed in
OL,10,Fhandcuffs moments before he became
OL,11,Funconscious and subsequently died.
OL,13,FA longer transcript of the footage
OL,14,Freleased by the Crown Prosecution
OL,15,FService, first obtained by the BBC,
OL,16,Freveals the moment officers realised
OL,17,FMr Nowak had been stabbed.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
