PN,38603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1782371886
OL,3,CTranscript reveals moment police
OL,4,Cdiscovered Henry Nowak had been stabbed
OL,6,FDigwa had told police attending the
OL,7,Fscene of the stabbing in Southampton
OL,8,Fin December last year that he had been
OL,9,Fthe victim of a racist attack.
OL,11,FIn body-worn camera footage from the
OL,12,Fincident, Mr Nowak can be heard
OL,13,Frepeatedly saying: "I've been
OL,14,Fstabbed," to which an officer replies:
OL,15,F"You've been stabbed? Whereabouts?
OL,16,FDon't think you have, mate."
OL,26,@uD@TOUvD@IO]wD@AOUxD@\O]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
