FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1782371886
OL,3,CTranscript reveals moment police
OL,4,Cdiscovered Henry Nowak had been stabbed
OL,6,FThe female officer replies: "Yes, he's
OL,7,Fgot a stab... there's a mark there."
OL,9,FPolice officer one adds: "That makes
OL,10,Fit worse. He's got a stab... I'm
OL,11,Fpushing on a stab wound."
OL,13,FThe female officer says: "That's okay.
OL,14,FIt's fine... It's not coming out. It's
OL,15,Ffine. Keep going. Keep going. It's not
OL,16,Fbleeding out."
OL,18,FPolice officer one continues chest
OL,19,Fcompressions and then a paramedic
OL,20,Farrives on the scene.
OL,26,@nD@]OUoD@dO]qD@ZOUsD@YO]uD@ZOUxD@NO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/9
