PN,38607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1782371886
OL,3,CTranscript reveals moment police
OL,4,Cdiscovered Henry Nowak had been stabbed
OL,6,FPolice officer one tells him "we just
OL,7,Fdiscovered a stab wound in his chest".
OL,9,FThe recording ends after eight minutes
OL,10,Fand 49 seconds.
OL,12,FIt was released with no objection from
OL,13,FMr Nowak's family, and after
OL,14,Fconsultation with Hampshire Police.
OL,26,@nD@^OUoD@eO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/9
