OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1782371886
OL,3,CTranscript reveals moment police
OL,4,Cdiscovered Henry Nowak had been stabbed
OL,6,FFollowing the case, temporary Deputy
OL,7,FChief Constable Robert France, of
OL,8,FHampshire Constabulary, apologised on
OL,9,Fbehalf of the officers, but said they
OL,10,Fwere "lied to" and would have been
OL,11,Funaware of Mr Nowak's injury which he
OL,12,Fsaid would not have been obvious.
OL,14,FHe said: "This is an absolutely tragic
OL,15,Fcase, and my sympathies are absolutely
OL,16,Fwith Henry's family, his friends, and
OL,17,Fhis loved ones.
OL,26,@rD@FOUrD@NO]vD@JOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1782371886
OL,3,CTranscript reveals moment police
OL,4,Cdiscovered Henry Nowak had been stabbed
OL,6,F"I want to apologise, I want to say
OL,7,Fthat I am sorry that Henry couldn't be
OL,8,Fsaved that night. I'm sorry that he
OL,9,Fwas handcuffed and arrested in the
OL,10,Fmoments before he lost consciousness."
OL,12,FThe Independent Office for Police
OL,13,FConduct is investigating Hampshire
OL,14,FPolice's response in Mr Nowak's case.
OL,16,FThe jury inquest into his death next
OL,17,Fyear at Winchester Coroner's Court
OL,18,Fwill also look at whether any "act or
OL,19,Fomission by a police officer" caused
OL,20,For contributed to his death.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@fO]zD@_OU{D@]O]
